                <h1>Does a Diversion Show on Background Checks?</h1>
                <p>When it comes to background checks, diversion programs may or may not show up depending on the specifics of the check. In general, successful completion of a diversion program can lead to the charges being dismissed, and these records sealed. However, certain employers or agencies may still have access to these records.</p>
